title: DDFP 348: 2015 NFL schedule 360
itunes:title: DDFP 348: 2015 NFL schedule 360
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Elliot Harrison for a full breakdown of the 2015 NFL schedule. The guys debate early-season matchups to watch (9:29); which 2014 playoff team is in danger of missing the playoffs (15:13); teams poised for surprising fast starts (21:33) and more. Also, Shek's reaction to Tim Tebow signing with the Eagles.
